@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_quogbt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.16
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.40)) * wp.exp((v1 + 0.87 + v0 + 0.06)))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.29) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.59)) / wp.sin((v2 + 0.28 - v2 + 0.96)))
    v0 = 0.29
    v0 = v0
    v0 = (tmp / wp.exp((v1 + 0.46 + v0 + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
